NK047(tsi)005:0: don rnam par nges pa 'di 'chad pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:3: yongs su rdzogs pa mjug don gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:5: dang por dge ba rtsom pa'i yan lag /
NK047(tsi)005:6: bar du dge ba brtsam bya'i don /
NK047(tsi)005:7: tha mar dge ba mjug gi don gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:9: dam bca' gnyis tshigs bcad re res so //
NK047(tsi)005:13: de ltar gzhal ba'i 'bras bu bstan pa gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:15: sangs rgyas rnams kyis gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:16: rigs pa gnyis su mdor bstan /
NK047(tsi)005:17: rigs pa bzhis rgyas par bshad pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:19: bden pa gnyis kyi gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:21: de'i byed las rton pa bzhi /
NK047(tsi)005:22: 'bras bu spobs pa'i gter chen brgyad bshad pa'o //
NK047(tsi)005:24: rigs pa snga ma gsum bshad /
NK047(tsi)005:27: snang ba rten 'brel du spyir bstan /
NK047(tsi)005:28: de'i rgyu 'bras ngo bo nyid kyi rigs pa bye brag tu bshad /
NK047(tsi)005:29: de gsum mthun par don bsdu ba'o //
NK047(tsi)005:31: ji ltar snang ba gnyis pa la bya byed dang ltos pa'i rigs pa bshad /
NK047(tsi)005:32: chos nyid kyi rigs pa bshad pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:37: rgyu yi tshogs pa gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:38: des na rgyu dang gnyis pa chos nyid rigs pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:39: snang ba kun rdzob kyi sgo nas bshad /
NK047(tsi)005:40: stong pa don dam gyi sgo nas bshad pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:43: de yi rnam par bzhag pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:46: chos gcig la yang gnyis pa don dam gyi sgo nas bshad pa /
NK047(tsi)005:47: de ltar rgyu 'bras gsum pa don bsdu /
NK047(tsi)005:48: bya ba byed dang gnyis pa 'thad sgrub la /
NK047(tsi)005:52: de ltar bden gnyis gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:54: rjes su dpag pa'i 'thad sgrub gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:55: dang po la spyir bstan pa dang /
NK047(tsi)005:59: mngon sum nyid ni gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:65: dbang po lnga las skyes gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:66: yid dbang las skyes gsum pa /
NK047(tsi)005:67: lung bzhin legs par bzhi pa /
NK047(tsi)005:68: mngon sum myong bas gsum pa don bsdu /
NK047(tsi)005:69: rjes dpag mngon sum gnyis pa rjes dpag la /
NK047(tsi)005:74: blo gang gis rjes su dpag pa /
NK047(tsi)005:75: rtags gang las rjes su dpag pa /
NK047(tsi)005:76: tshul ji ltar rjes su dpag pa gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:78: yul rnams don gyi gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:79: gang la brten nas gsum pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:80: gzhal bya'i sgo nas gsum du bzhag pa /
NK047(tsi)005:81: sgrub tshul gyi sgo nas bzhir bzhag pa /
NK047(tsi)005:82: 'jug tshul gyi sgo nas gnyis su bzhag pa'o //
NK047(tsi)005:84: yang dag du na gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:85: sgrub pa'i rnam pa gsum pa /
NK047(tsi)005:86: tshad ma la brten gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:91: tha snyad pa'i tshad ma dang /
NK047(tsi)005:92: don dam dpyod byed kyi tshad ma'i dbye ba gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:94: tha snyad la yang gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:95: don dam la yang gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:96: snga ma la brten gsum pa rtsod spong la /
NK047(tsi)005:101: mi dgos pa'i rtsod spong gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:103: rtog pa med dang gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:104: yang dag nyid du gsum pa /
NK047(tsi)005:105: tshad ma tshad min gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:107: don dam dpyod byed la rtsod pa spang /
NK047(tsi)005:108: mthun par don bsdu ba gsum /
NK047(tsi)005:110: tha snyad tshad ma gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:113: gzhal bya kun rdzob bden pa /
NK047(tsi)005:115: de'i byed las ston pa bzhi la /
NK047(tsi)005:117: bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:121: gang zag la mi rton chos la ston pa bzhi po rim par /
NK047(tsi)005:122: des na gang zag chos la thos bsam don la
NK047(tsi)005:123: rnam par dpe don du rnams su sogs kyis bstan
NK047(tsi)005:124: / gsum pa 'bras bu spobs pa'i gter brgyad bshad pa la /
NK047(tsi)005:125: de ltar bden gnyis sogs kyis bstan /
NK047(tsi)005:126: gsum pa de ltar gzhal ba'i 'bras bu /
NK047(tsi)005:128: gsum pa tha mar dge ba 'jug don la /
NK047(tsi)005:130: de dag gi dge ba bsngo ba gnyis /
NK047(tsi)005:132: gzigs pa shin tu gnyis pa /
NK047(tsi)005:135: 'jam dpal smra ba'i nyi ma zhes sogs /
